---
title: Connect Flow (Authorization + Account Creation)
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant D as Dapp SDK
    participant I as Iframe (PXE)
    participant P as Popup
    participant A as Authenticator

    D->>I: encrypt(keyA, { method: "connect" })
    I->>P: window.open("wallet.aztec.network/auth")

    alt First visit
        P->>A: credentials.create() + PRF
        A-->>P: publicKey(x,y) + credentialId + PRF(32B)
        P->>P: HKDF(PRF) → accountSalt + protocol keys
        P->>I: postMessage({ publicKey, credentialId, accountSalt })
        I->>I: Compute address from publicKey
        I->>I: Store credentialId + publicKey in IndexedDB
        I->>I: Init PXE, register account, begin sync
    else Returning visit
        P->>A: credentials.get() + PRF
        A-->>P: PRF(32B) — biometric required
        P->>P: HKDF(PRF) → encryption key
        P->>I: postMessage({ encryptionKey })
        I->>I: Load credentialId + publicKey from IndexedDB
        I->>I: Decrypt PXE cache, resume from checkpoint
    end

    I-->>D: encrypt(keyB, { result: { address } })
